Class ParameterTypeDynamicCategory<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rapidminer.parameter.ParameterType
      • com.rapidminer.parameter.ParameterTypeSingle
        • com.rapidminer.parameter.ParameterTypeCategory
          • org.rapidprom.parameter.ParameterTypeDynamicCategory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - indicates what underlying java object the user wants to choose.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ParameterTypeExampleSetAttributesDynamicCategory, ParameterTypeXEventClassifierCategory

    public abstract class ParameterTypeDynamicCategory<T>
extends com.rapidminer.parameter.ParameterTypeCategory
    The ParameterTypeDynamicCategory, allows us to change the contents of a ParameterTypeCategory, depending on some inputPort's meta data. Additionally this class introduces the option to query, given the selected index, what the corresponding object is.

    svzelst
